rComments: If you have the chance to take a music class, take one from him. I have learn so much from him about education that it has changed my perspective greatly. He really does care for his students and wants to improve himself and the class. If you ever have a problem with the class or just a random problem in general, he will listen to you. Great prof

Dr. Kruse facilitates great discussion. This class is only difficult in the fact that it challenges you to think. There is not a textbook, but lots of readings. I'm not sure if he always teaches this class. He is an overall amazing teacher.
